FBIS4-31169 "dreeu108_k_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-108 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 CROATIA Kuna Supersedes Dinar as Legal Tender Kuna Supersedes Dinar as Legal Tender LD0606083194 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 0800 GMT 6 Jun 94 LD0606083194 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network English BFN [Text] From today the only legal tender in Croatia is the kuna. According to a government decision, the dinar is no longer valid for payments but may be exchanged for kuna in banks and post offices until the end of the year.
